 the total economic cost of equity awards exceeds the expensed amounts shown in the segment reconciliations.\n\n## Summary\n\nThe company discloses share-based compensation **both** by segment (in the Segment Adjusted EBITDA reconciliation tables) **and** by income-statement line item (in the notes). It is consistently treated as an add-back/exclusion in Segment Adjusted EBITDA across all periods and segments, with the AI segment being the primary driver of the rapid overall growth in this expense.',
